Program Name, Category, Keywords:
---------------------------------

   Dschump! action puzzle game.  Keywords: adlib,game,dschump
   homebrew,puzzle,strategy,vga.


Short Description:
------------------

   Dschump! distributed by HomeBrew Software.  Dschump! is a
   fast 'action'/puzzle solving game from South Africa.  The
   shareware version has 20 levels, MIDI, and digitized sound.
   Joystick support. VGA, 500K RAM required. (v1.4)    <ASP>


Long Description:
-----------------

   Dschump! distributed by HomeBrew Software.  Dschump! is a
   fast 'action'/puzzle solving game from South Africa.  The
   shareware version has 20 levels, MIDI, and digitized sound.
   Registered users get 100 more levels, a hint sheet and
   passwords to skip to a level. Joystick support. VGA, 500K
   RAM required. (v1.4)                                <ASP>


Registration Information:
-------------------------

   Registered users get the latest version of the complete Dschump!
   game (containing 100 levels) along with the password to move to
   levels.

   For complete user registration information please refer to the
   ORDER.FRM text file.








